OL,3,CMan, 65, 'seriously injured' in crash
OL,4,Cas police launch investigation
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,7,Ffollowing a serious crash in the
OL,8,FScottish Borders which saw a man taken
OL,9,Fto hospital with serious injuries.
OL,11,FThe crash happened on the B6357 at
OL,12,FBonchester Bridge, south east of
OL,13,FHawick, on Saturday 11 October, at
OL,14,Faround 1pm.
OL,16,FPolice have said the incident involved
OL,17,Fa bronze BMW R1250 motorcycle.
