OL,3,CMan, 65, 'seriously injured' in crash
OL,4,Cas police launch investigation
OL,6,FEmergency services attended the scene,
OL,7,Fand the rider, a 65-year-old man, was
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital with serious
OL,9,Finjuries. Officers have said his
OL,10,Fcondition is described as serious.
OL,12,FThe road was closed for a short time.
OL,14,FSergeant Michael Shillington, from
OL,15,FPolice Scotland, said: "Our enquiries
OL,16,Fare ongoing to establish the full
OL,17,Fcircumstances and we are asking any
OL,18,Fother road users on the B6357 around
OL,19,Fthe time of the crash to get in touch.
